## PAGE STRUCTURE

NAVBAR (sticky top):
- Logo: "ColdPing" bold, blue dot after the g
- Right: "Join Waitlist" button

HERO SECTION:
- Badge: "Powered by Gemini AI"
- H1: "Cold emails that actually get replies"
- Subtext: "Paste a LinkedIn profile → get a hyper-personalized email in 3 seconds. Free."
- Stats: "3 sec generation" and "Free to use"

THE TOOL (two-column desktop, single column mobile):
LEFT — Inputs:
- Textarea: "Paste LinkedIn profile text"
- Input: "Your product or service"
- Input: "Your CTA"
- Select: Tone — Friendly & casual / Professional / Direct & bold
- Button: "Generate Email →"

RIGHT — Output:
- Placeholder: dashed border, "Your personalized email will appear here"
- After generation: subject line + email body + Copy button + score badge
- Loading: spinner + pulse animation

HOW IT WORKS (3 steps):
1. Paste LinkedIn
2. Add your details
3. Get your email

WAITLIST SECTION:
- POST to https://formspree.io/f/${FORMSPREE_ID}
- Success: "You're on the list!" in green
- Error: "Something went wrong." in red

FOOTER:
- "ColdPing © 2026"
- "Built with Gemini AI + Antigravity"
- Dark bg #0F172A, white text


## IMPORTANT
- GEMINI_API_KEY has NO NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix — server-side only
- .env.local must be in .gitignore
- Tailwind v4 uses @import "tailwindcss" in globals.css
- Copy button changes to "Copied!" for 2 seconds then reverts
- Fully mobile responsive
